precis:
Amendment to the INDIAN BRIDGE WORKERS REMISSION ORDER remitting income tax
on bridge pay until the litigation is resolved and remitting income taxes,
from 1984 until the resolution, of other taxpayers, such as spouses and
children, accruing because of the inclusion of the bridge pay in the income
of the Indians.
